trans-unit.source: Provides a visual editor to edit <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelItem" name="ModelItem" href=""></xref> objects, and provides an area for the user to drag and drop, and otherwise edit composed elements.
trans-unit.target: Gir et visual redigeringsprogram for å redigere <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelItem" name="ModelItem" href=""> </xref> objekter, og et område for brukeren å dra og slipp og redigere ellers består elementer.

trans-unit.source: This is a WPF control that acts as an editing container that displays the visualization for the data it is bound to in the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemPresenter.Item%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en WPF-kontroll som fungerer som en redigering beholder som viser visualiseringen dataene den er bundet til i den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemPresenter.Item%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemPresenter.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: The WorkflowItemPresenter is one of two controls (the other being <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemsPresenter>) that can be used to create a container for visualizing and editing a composed element.
trans-unit.target: WorkflowItemPresenter er en av to kontroller (den andre som <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemsPresenter>) som kan brukes til å opprette en beholder for å visualisere og redigere et sammensatt element.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowItemsPresenter>

trans-unit.source: It is important to note that the visualization of the composed element is not controlled by the WorkflowItemPresenter but it renders with the visualization associated in the metadata store for a given type.
trans-unit.target: Det er viktig å være klar over at visualisering av elementet består ikke kontrolleres av WorkflowItemPresenter, men den gjengir med visualiseringen tilknyttede i store metadata for en gitt type.

trans-unit.source: The WorkflowItemPresenter is a specialized subclass of the [!INCLUDE[avalon1](~/add/includes/avalon1-md.md)]<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl> that has been modified to support drag and drop, copy and paste, and other visual editing actions.
trans-unit.target: WorkflowItemPresenter er en spesiell underklasse av den [!INCLUDE[avalon1](~/add/includes/avalon1-md.md)] <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>som har blitt endret til å støtte dra og slipp, Kopier og Lim inn og andre visuelle redigeringshandlinger.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>
